  "detailed_description": "MEMOLOGY is a comprehensive test that shows how deeply you are immersed in the culture of memes. In the game you will find many international, new or already classic memes, such as: Pepe, Dogi and so on, but MEMOLOGY is still recommended for people who are at least a little familiar with the Russian language, as there are a lot of Russian memes and references in the tests.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Wide Putin, Narrow Putin, Dancing Putin<br></li><li> Cats and other Internet symbols<br></li><li> Bouncy soundtrack</li></ul>",
